item.description:
Join us for dinner and drinks at California Pizza Kitchen located inside the Natick Collection, near Macy's. CPK has a fun menu with lots of good food at reasonable prices. Meet new, friendly and interesting people and have a fun and relaxing evening. We always have a good time!

Everyone pays for their own food/drink. If you have trouble finding us, please call Catherine at 774 232 0000. Look forward to seeing you there!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo) inside ent. If need to, please call 774 232 0000
item.name: Dinner and Drinks at California Pizza Kitchen, Natick
